OL,3,C20 of Guernsey's finest to head to
OL,4,CGlasgow for Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FGuernsey has announced it will be
OL,7,Fsending a team of 20 athletes to
OL,8,FGlasgow to compete across four sports
OL,9,Fin the Commonwealth Games this summer.
OL,11,FScheduled to take place between 23
OL,12,FJuly and 2 August, the Games are the
OL,13,Fhighest level of competition at which
OL,14,Flocal athletes can represent the
OL,15,Fislands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
