OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774023077
OL,3,C20 of Guernsey's finest to head to
OL,4,CGlasgow for Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FGlasgow previously hosted the Games in
OL,7,F2014, and stepped in at the last
OL,8,Fminute to host this year's competition
OL,9,Fafter Victoria in Australia decided to
OL,10,Fwithdraw in September 2024.
OL,12,FIt means this year's Games will be a
OL,13,Fsmaller-scale event, with fewer sports
OL,14,Fand events included - something the
OL,15,FGuernsey Commonwealth Games
OL,16,FAssociation Council (GCGAC) has
OL,17,Fdescribed as "a rather challenging and
OL,18,Fon occasion frustrating" thing to
OL,19,Fnavigate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
