OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774023077
OL,3,C20 of Guernsey's finest to head to
OL,4,CGlasgow for Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FThese difficulties saw 2022 silver
OL,7,Fmedalist Lucy Beere decide to withdraw
OL,8,Ffrom competing in the Bowls earlier
OL,9,Fthis month.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News: "I found myself
OL,12,Fnavigating a complex and, at times,
OL,13,Funclear eligibility process.
OL,15,F"After a prolonged period seeking
OL,16,Fclarification regarding my
OL,17,Feligibility, it was ultimately
OL,18,Fconfirmed that I was eligible to
OL,19,Ftrial. However, by that stage, the
OL,20,Fprocess had taken a significant
OL,21,Fpersonal toll."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
