PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1774023077
OL,3,C20 of Guernsey's finest to head to
OL,4,CGlasgow for Commonwealth Games
OL,6,FSome of the missing sports and
OL,7,Fdisciplines this year include the
OL,8,FMarathon, Lawn Bowls, Road Cycling,
OL,9,FShooting, and the Triathlon.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Peter Jory, Chef de
OL,12,FMission at the GCGAC, said: "I am
OL,13,Fextremely pleased to be able to
OL,14,Fsupport a wonderful group of talented
OL,15,Fathletes at the Games.
OL,17,F"We will embrace the challenges of the
OL,18,Fmulti-cultural and multi-sport Games
OL,19,Fthat we expect to progress for future
OL,20,FGames."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
